 |INTERMITTENT HUNG PORTS ON SIO ASYNC.                                       |
 |           SUGGESTED SOLUTION/DESCRIPTION OF PATCH:                         |
 |CHANGE THE INIT AND HANG/ANSWER LOGIC TO DELAY DURING THE ENABLE SEQ.       |
